  "prompt": "How long does a Swiffer Sweeper vac replacement battery usually last?",
  "response": "The battery life of a Swiffer Sweeper Vac replacement battery can vary depending on usage, but generally, it lasts for about 30 to 60 minutes of continuous cleaning on a full charge. Factors such as carpet vs. hard floor cleaning, the presence of large debris, and the specific model of the Swiffer can also influence battery duration. It's advisable to recharge it after every use to ensure optimal performance.",
